I’m back in LA to kick off FRIEZE Art Week in a big way! I’ll be DJing opening night for the legendary artist Ernie Barnes, “Where Music and Soul Live” exhibit.

This will include 30 works that span street scenes, portraits of musicians, and images of dancers in nightclubs. Some of these pieces are coming from private collectors who have never exhibited these works publicly.
